1
00:01:32,425 --> 00:01:37,012
(Zhan Zhao Adventures)

2
00:01:37,101 --> 00:01:40,032
(Episode 33)

3
00:01:44,216 --> 00:01:45,822
I'm not good at comforting people.

4
00:01:47,255 --> 00:01:49,021
Yesterday, we managed to save your life,

5
00:01:50,096 --> 00:01:52,261
- but... - The medicine is bitter enough.

6
00:01:52,975 --> 00:01:56,061
No need for harsh words.

7
00:01:58,736 --> 00:01:59,736
Don't worry.

8
00:02:00,136 --> 00:02:03,078
I'll be more careful with my life from now on.

9
00:02:22,615 --> 00:02:23,942
I want to ask you for a favor.

10
00:02:25,022 --> 00:02:26,347
When Ming Zhu Er comes back,

11
00:02:26,616 --> 00:02:28,164
don't ask about what happened last night.

12
00:02:28,188 --> 00:02:29,674
And never bring up

13
00:02:30,215 --> 00:02:31,542
that I used to be a Yaksha.

14
00:02:36,376 --> 00:02:37,376
Zhan.

15
00:02:37,976 --> 00:02:39,982
Last time we talked about Zhao Yue An,

16
00:02:40,615 --> 00:02:41,902
we noticed

17
00:02:42,256 --> 00:02:43,902
you didn't want Ming Zhu Er to know.

18
00:02:44,215 --> 00:02:45,215
Why is that?

19
00:02:45,735 --> 00:02:47,655
The person who showed up at the yamen last night

20
00:02:48,256 --> 00:02:49,279
was Zhou Ji Liang.

21
00:02:51,015 --> 00:02:53,839
He was also a Yaksha.

22
00:02:59,095 --> 00:03:00,421
You weren't the only Yaksha?

23
00:03:06,015 --> 00:03:07,855
Back then, I was obsessed with being a Yaksha.

24
00:03:08,575 --> 00:03:10,701
I thought I was carrying out justice for heaven.

25
00:03:11,855 --> 00:03:14,861
I was addicted to the praise from the people for Yaksha.

26
00:03:15,416 --> 00:03:16,416
My actions

27
00:03:17,176 --> 00:03:18,661
became more reckless.

28
00:03:19,536 --> 00:03:20,861
Until one day,

29
00:03:22,655 --> 00:03:24,501
I found a brothel hideout.

30
00:03:25,696 --> 00:03:26,696
There,

31
00:03:27,295 --> 00:03:29,342
I ran into Zhou Ji Liang.

32
00:03:33,696 --> 00:03:35,102
You showed up late.

33
00:03:35,575 --> 00:03:37,616
I beat you to it this time.

34
00:03:37,696 --> 00:03:39,336
So, you are pretending to be me.

35
00:03:39,416 --> 00:03:40,416
Don't get mad.

36
00:03:40,655 --> 00:03:42,182
I'm basically you.

37
00:03:42,375 --> 00:03:43,622
I'm also a Yaksha.

38
00:03:44,015 --> 00:03:45,336
We're not enemies.

39
00:03:45,416 --> 00:03:46,695
In the town below the mountain,

40
00:03:46,775 --> 00:03:48,615
the scamming fortune teller

41
00:03:48,938 --> 00:03:50,344
and the cloth thief.

42
00:03:50,455 --> 00:03:51,775
Did you kill all of them?

43
00:03:51,855 --> 00:03:53,838
That's right. I did all of it.

44
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:56,680
Bad people should get what they deserve.

45
00:03:56,855 --> 00:03:58,974
That's how Yaksha does things.

46
00:03:59,175 --> 00:04:01,551
Are you out of your mind? They didn't deserve to die for that.

47
00:04:01,575 --> 00:04:03,981
What you and I did was already outside the law.

48
00:04:04,335 --> 00:04:06,599
Are we supposed to rank bad people by degrees?

49
00:04:06,855 --> 00:04:09,462
Honestly, you should hand over the Yaksha name to me.

50
00:04:09,775 --> 00:04:11,981
I'm more fit to be Yaksha than you.

51
00:04:16,416 --> 00:04:18,118
- Help! - Help!

52
00:04:31,376 --> 00:04:32,376
Don't be scared.

53
00:04:32,656 --> 00:04:33,678
I'm here to help you.

54
00:04:45,096 --> 00:04:46,118
What's your name?

55
00:04:46,416 --> 00:04:47,416
Where do you live?

56
00:04:47,735 --> 00:04:49,416
My name's Yue Er.

57
00:04:49,496 --> 00:04:50,742
I live in Ming Village.

58
00:04:51,895 --> 00:04:53,501
This girl, Yue Er,

59
00:04:54,855 --> 00:04:56,501
is Ming Zhu Er's older sister.

60
00:04:59,256 --> 00:05:02,295
Later, I took those girls back to their homes.

61
00:05:03,730 --> 00:05:06,537
But Zhou Ji Liang either believed rumors

62
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,639
or made excuses for his killings to justify himself.

63
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,326
He claimed those girls

64
00:05:11,976 --> 00:05:13,661
were all sold by their parents

65
00:05:14,335 --> 00:05:15,661
to the brothel hideout.

66
00:05:18,416 --> 00:05:20,182
He found the girls' families

67
00:05:23,216 --> 00:05:24,439
and slaughtered them.

68
00:05:25,096 --> 00:05:27,862
Then, Ming Zhu Er's family was also killed by Zhou Ji Liang.

69
00:05:48,313 --> 00:05:49,313
Mom...

70
00:05:50,895 --> 00:05:51,895
Dad...

71
00:05:52,615 --> 00:05:54,582
Mom...

72
00:06:17,535 --> 00:06:18,599
I just hope

73
00:06:19,736 --> 00:06:21,936
he never remembers what happened back then.

74
00:06:23,655 --> 00:06:25,421
Just let him believe Yaksha was a bad guy.

75
00:06:26,938 --> 00:06:28,218
There's nothing wrong with that.

76
00:06:34,736 --> 00:06:36,535
Young master, you're awake.

77
00:06:43,215 --> 00:06:44,215
Young master.

78
00:06:48,696 --> 00:06:50,062
I heard you cried all night.

79
00:06:51,056 --> 00:06:52,296
My cries woke you up.

80
00:06:52,376 --> 00:06:53,376
That was worth it.

81
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:57,207
Young master, I've figured it out.

82
00:06:57,288 --> 00:06:59,448
Zhou Ji Liang was trying to stir things up between us.

83
00:06:59,616 --> 00:07:02,798
I shouldn't have listened to his nonsense and then pressured you.

84
00:07:09,095 --> 00:07:10,871
Young master. Look, what do you think this is?

85
00:07:10,895 --> 00:07:13,418
While the yamen was empty, Zhao Zhi Er and I snuck this out.

86
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,480
Nobody was there?

87
00:07:15,256 --> 00:07:16,438
How could the yamen be empty?

88
00:07:33,941 --> 00:07:35,441
Something unexpected happened last night.

89
00:07:35,465 --> 00:07:36,664
I wrote everything down.

90
00:07:36,813 --> 00:07:40,341
I think what happened ten years ago is nothing as we thought.

91
00:07:42,015 --> 00:07:43,575
Get the message out as soon as you can.

92
00:07:43,772 --> 00:07:45,178
Remember, make it fast.

93
00:07:52,179 --> 00:07:54,408
Sect Leader Tang, you're out gathering herbs this early?

94
00:07:54,432 --> 00:07:55,831
I'm heading back to Tang Sect.

95
00:07:55,897 --> 00:07:58,081
Before I leave, I'll prepare some herbs for Zhan.

96
00:08:01,076 --> 00:08:02,933
Tang, thanks for saving my life last night.

97
00:08:03,022 --> 00:08:04,063
No need to thank me.

98
00:08:04,126 --> 00:08:05,527
Compared to Doctor Bai,

99
00:08:05,605 --> 00:08:07,685
what I did last night was nothing but a minor trick.

100
00:08:11,792 --> 00:08:14,009
Once I get back to Tang Sect, I'll look for a new solution

101
00:08:14,033 --> 00:08:15,433
to cure the At First Sight poison.

102
00:08:15,514 --> 00:08:18,194
If there's any progress, I'll definitely write to let you all know.

103
00:08:18,355 --> 00:08:19,956
All right. Doctor Tang.

104
00:08:20,022 --> 00:08:21,222
We'll see you out of the city.

105
00:08:21,302 --> 00:08:22,502
No need to trouble yourselves.

106
00:08:22,655 --> 00:08:24,741
I'm afraid you still have important things to do.

107
00:08:24,936 --> 00:08:26,376
Go check out the excitement outside.

108
00:08:26,736 --> 00:08:28,856
Lord Hu is putting on a show again.

109
00:08:48,176 --> 00:08:49,575
I promised everyone

110
00:08:49,655 --> 00:08:51,536
to explain the two previous murder cases

111
00:08:51,616 --> 00:08:52,861
and give everyone an answer.

112
00:08:53,296 --> 00:08:54,296
Now,

113
00:08:54,535 --> 00:08:56,421
the Xiuluo Sect leader is seriously injured.

114
00:08:56,775 --> 00:08:59,215
The two killers have also been captured.

115
00:08:59,496 --> 00:09:01,656
As the magistrate of Wanshan County,

116
00:09:01,736 --> 00:09:03,101
I have kept my word.

117
00:09:03,335 --> 00:09:05,062
I've kept the peace in our county.

118
00:09:05,335 --> 00:09:07,056
According to the laws of the Song Dynasty,

119
00:09:07,136 --> 00:09:09,056
a murderer must pay with their life.

120
00:09:09,136 --> 00:09:13,656
Today, I will execute these two killers right here and now.

121
00:09:13,736 --> 00:09:16,262
First, to bring justice for the victims.

122
00:09:16,355 --> 00:09:21,421
Secondly, to warn those who dare threaten Wanshan County.

123
00:09:21,813 --> 00:09:23,419
Anyone who crosses Wanshan County

124
00:09:23,895 --> 00:09:26,176
will pay for their crimes with blood.

125
00:09:26,256 --> 00:09:27,536
Blood for blood!

126
00:09:27,616 --> 00:09:28,856
Blood for blood!

127
00:09:28,936 --> 00:09:30,176
Blood for blood!

128
00:09:30,256 --> 00:09:31,621
Blood for blood!

129
00:09:53,736 --> 00:09:55,582
He finally played

130
00:09:57,056 --> 00:09:58,621
the last move of this game.

131
00:10:16,576 --> 00:10:17,576
Lord Hu.

132
00:10:23,522 --> 00:10:25,002
What an impressive show of authority.

133
00:10:25,616 --> 00:10:28,079
It's been ages since I've seen such a huge performance.

134
00:10:28,397 --> 00:10:30,688
You act better than any performer.

135
00:10:39,655 --> 00:10:40,878
Good thing you're fine.

136
00:10:41,230 --> 00:10:44,235
Last night, I was really afraid you wouldn't make it.

137
00:10:46,351 --> 00:10:47,871
You've been planning this for so long,

138
00:10:48,015 --> 00:10:49,422
all for me, right?

139
00:10:49,775 --> 00:10:51,141
To play this game with you,

140
00:10:51,775 --> 00:10:53,221
I have to stay alive.

141
00:11:04,879 --> 00:11:06,725
Now, I finally understand

142
00:11:07,576 --> 00:11:10,621
how the peace under your rule really came to be, Lord Hu.

143
00:11:11,015 --> 00:11:14,342
If you want a reputation for swift justice and solving cases like a god,

144
00:11:14,935 --> 00:11:18,542
the easiest way is to commit the crime and solve it yourself.

145
00:11:19,256 --> 00:11:20,981
I bet when you first took office,

146
00:11:21,336 --> 00:11:25,221
the Xiuluo Sect was making poison in the county and holding cult rituals

147
00:11:26,415 --> 00:11:28,302
was all your doing, wasn't it?

148
00:11:29,136 --> 00:11:31,621
Later, you staged arrests.

149
00:11:31,855 --> 00:11:36,061
That's how your reputation as Justice Hu spread throughout the county.

150
00:11:38,188 --> 00:11:39,828
We're both officials here.

151
00:11:39,909 --> 00:11:43,782
You should know that I'm not the only one who used this method.

152
00:11:44,096 --> 00:11:48,861
If I don't establish authority, who would listen to a mere scholar like me?

153
00:11:50,895 --> 00:11:51,895
Lord Zhan,

154
00:11:52,456 --> 00:11:54,261
we may not be friends anymore,

155
00:11:54,456 --> 00:11:56,702
but we still share the bond of classmates, at least.

156
00:11:56,959 --> 00:11:59,600
Take my advice and leave Wanshan County.

157
00:11:59,681 --> 00:12:01,680
That's the only way to protect yourself

158
00:12:01,761 --> 00:12:03,368
and the people you care about.

159
00:12:11,976 --> 00:12:15,975
What happened between us shouldn't have involved Ming Zhu Er.

160
00:12:16,055 --> 00:12:17,998
I didn't want to drag him into this either.

161
00:12:18,079 --> 00:12:19,605
But I had no choice.

162
00:12:19,895 --> 00:12:21,735
Since you didn't care about your own life,

163
00:12:21,815 --> 00:12:24,221
I had no choice but to go after the people you care about.

164
00:12:24,355 --> 00:12:26,041
That's the only way to force you to leave.

165
00:12:33,208 --> 00:12:34,494
I've said all I can.

166
00:12:35,376 --> 00:12:38,342
Looks like you're still going to do things your way, Lord Zhan.

167
00:12:39,616 --> 00:12:42,462
Fine. If you want to stay, then stay.

168
00:12:42,775 --> 00:12:48,038
I want to see how much longer you'll manage to stay in my Wanshan County.

169
00:12:48,376 --> 00:12:50,021
Why wouldn't we be able to stay?

170
00:12:50,813 --> 00:12:52,500
I'm pretty comfortable in that house.

171
00:12:53,216 --> 00:12:54,656
Next time, get me a bigger one.

172
00:12:54,736 --> 00:12:56,221
I'll bring my sworn brother over too.

173
00:12:58,544 --> 00:13:00,270
I'll just retire here with you.

174
00:13:02,616 --> 00:13:03,861
Lord Hu!

175
00:13:09,655 --> 00:13:12,055
Sir, you should go take a look. Up in the mountains...

176
00:13:14,256 --> 00:13:15,376
The bodies on the mountains.

177
00:13:43,439 --> 00:13:45,999
Lord Zhan, this is a Wanshan County case.

178
00:13:46,063 --> 00:13:47,670
You don't need to get involved.

179
00:13:48,976 --> 00:13:50,575
My rank may not be as high as yours,

180
00:13:50,655 --> 00:13:52,656
but I'm still the head of this county, at least.

181
00:13:52,730 --> 00:13:54,130
As long as I'm in office,

182
00:13:54,230 --> 00:13:57,176
any case in Wanshan County has to go through me first.

183
00:13:57,272 --> 00:13:58,722
We're still going to investigate.

184
00:13:58,802 --> 00:13:59,855
What can you do?

185
00:14:00,230 --> 00:14:01,755
Your lackeys aren't even with you.

186
00:14:01,855 --> 00:14:03,380
You think you can take us on?

187
00:14:27,730 --> 00:14:28,730
Hurry.

188
00:14:33,415 --> 00:14:36,414
Buried here are the remains of our loved ones.

189
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,977
No one reported it to the authorities.

190
00:14:38,001 --> 00:14:39,521
What case do you think you're solving?

191
00:14:43,980 --> 00:14:44,980
Lord Zhan,

192
00:14:45,616 --> 00:14:48,221
you wouldn't turn your blade on the people, would you?

193
00:15:09,703 --> 00:15:11,743
Has everyone in the county heard the news?

194
00:15:11,813 --> 00:15:13,058
Yes, sir. Rest assured.

195
00:15:23,616 --> 00:15:25,976
The pelvic bones are narrow, so they're all male.

196
00:15:26,376 --> 00:15:27,662
The skulls and ribs are broken.

197
00:15:28,216 --> 00:15:30,496
It's the same way the young man died before.

198
00:15:32,105 --> 00:15:34,712
The key to this case must be the cause of death.

199
00:15:34,813 --> 00:15:36,733
Otherwise, Hu Xiao Chen, wouldn't be so nervous.

200
00:15:36,935 --> 00:15:40,141
He and the coroner were working together before and almost fooled us all.

201
00:15:40,563 --> 00:15:43,068
Let's go find Wang Qing and Liu Er Lang's bodies.

202
00:15:43,167 --> 00:15:44,687
If we're any later, it'll be too late.

203
00:15:44,719 --> 00:15:45,719
Wait.

204
00:15:47,096 --> 00:15:49,518
I'm afraid Hu Xiao Chen has already beaten us to it.

205
00:15:50,355 --> 00:15:52,796
Then, let's just go back and grab a body.

206
00:15:52,897 --> 00:15:54,815
We can't just let them destroy the evidence.

207
00:15:54,895 --> 00:15:56,221
If we take the body by force,

208
00:15:56,432 --> 00:15:58,037
we'll definitely clash with the people.

209
00:15:58,105 --> 00:15:59,688
That's exactly what Hu Xiao Chen wants.

210
00:16:01,479 --> 00:16:05,045
Do you remember where we found the lead on Zhao Yue An?

211
00:16:05,456 --> 00:16:06,479
Gucheng County?

212
00:16:08,736 --> 00:16:11,719
So you mean we should look for the body of Jin Niang's husband?

213
00:16:12,768 --> 00:16:13,768
That day,

214
00:16:14,175 --> 00:16:16,582
Hu Xiao Chen asked us what we found in Gucheng County?

215
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:20,339
We never mentioned that we've already found Duan Shi Lang's body.

216
00:16:20,932 --> 00:16:23,273
That's right. He doesn't know about this.

217
00:16:23,355 --> 00:16:25,401
He'd never think to destroy Duan Shi Lang's body.

218
00:16:26,216 --> 00:16:29,038
Take Ming Zhu Er and Zhao Zhi Er to Gucheng County first.

219
00:16:29,230 --> 00:16:31,310
Ling Long and I will stay in Wanshan County for now.

220
00:16:31,351 --> 00:16:32,511
We'll meet up with you later.

221
00:16:32,980 --> 00:16:34,701
You're worried Hu Xiao Chen will catch on

222
00:16:34,782 --> 00:16:36,027
so you're buying me time.

223
00:16:36,563 --> 00:16:37,626
That's part of it.

224
00:16:40,144 --> 00:16:42,861
But more importantly, I want to ask Lord Hu

225
00:16:43,376 --> 00:16:45,518
to clear up something for me.

226
00:16:56,655 --> 00:16:58,336
Come on, thanks for your hard work.

227
00:16:58,496 --> 00:17:00,056
Whatever Lord Hu asked us to do,

228
00:17:00,136 --> 00:17:01,822
we must do it right, don't we?

229
00:17:02,096 --> 00:17:03,096
He's here.

230
00:17:08,895 --> 00:17:09,895
Sir.

231
00:17:10,438 --> 00:17:12,764
Sir, all the bodies from the pit are here.

232
00:17:13,105 --> 00:17:15,192
The village has people watching over all the young people

233
00:17:15,216 --> 00:17:16,712
who've died in the county these years.

234
00:17:16,736 --> 00:17:17,736
Rest assured, sir.

235
00:17:18,063 --> 00:17:19,383
Thank you all for your hard work.

236
00:17:20,647 --> 00:17:22,693
Sir, don't mention it.

237
00:17:23,023 --> 00:17:24,663
We're just doing our part for the county.

238
00:17:24,730 --> 00:17:25,730
It's what we should do.

239
00:17:27,144 --> 00:17:30,188
Wang Qing and Liu Er Lang's bodies are here too.

240
00:17:30,496 --> 00:17:33,312
Wang Qing and Liu Er Lang's families were all killed by the Xiuluo Sect.

241
00:17:33,336 --> 00:17:34,581
No one's watching over their bodies.

242
00:17:34,605 --> 00:17:36,278
We were worried Zhan Zhao would take advantage,

243
00:17:36,302 --> 00:17:39,844
so we just took care of the matter ourselves before your orders.

244
00:17:40,456 --> 00:17:42,021
Any news on Zhan Zhao?

245
00:17:42,256 --> 00:17:43,501
Has anyone seen him?

246
00:17:43,695 --> 00:17:46,576
We saw him at Wang Qing's grave.

247
00:17:46,808 --> 00:17:48,809
He and that girl went into the mountains.

248
00:17:48,897 --> 00:17:52,128
He said he wanted to search for the bodies

249
00:17:52,209 --> 00:17:53,529
according to Zhu Ming Yan's list.

250
00:17:53,616 --> 00:17:55,261
Let them search all they want.

251
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:57,622
This time, they'll be searching for a while.

252
00:17:58,136 --> 00:18:00,582
Only Zhan Zhao and Huo Ling Long are looking?

253
00:18:01,096 --> 00:18:03,455
- What about Bai Yu Tang? - He left the city.

254
00:18:03,535 --> 00:18:06,416
When my wife brought me lunch, she saw him at the city gate.

255
00:18:06,496 --> 00:18:08,935
I guess he couldn't find anything in the city,

256
00:18:09,015 --> 00:18:11,302
so he just went outside to look for the bodies.

257
00:18:12,376 --> 00:18:14,221
Left the city to search for bodies?

258
00:18:18,775 --> 00:18:20,775
The missing youth case in Gucheng County back then

259
00:18:20,976 --> 00:18:22,136
was connected to Zhao Yue An.

260
00:18:22,775 --> 00:18:25,422
Ten years ago, he killed Jin Niang to silence her.

261
00:18:26,535 --> 00:18:30,062
Why was he so sure Jin Niang was killed to keep her quiet?

262
00:18:32,136 --> 00:18:34,422
What did Jin Niang find out back then?

263
00:18:36,815 --> 00:18:39,501
Did she find her husband, Duan Shi Lang?

264
00:18:44,895 --> 00:18:46,861
But if they already found Duan Shi Lang's body,

265
00:18:47,296 --> 00:18:49,901
why didn't he go to Gucheng County with Bai Yu Tang?

266
00:18:55,136 --> 00:18:58,861
He told everyone he was heading into the mountains to search for bodies.

267
00:19:00,735 --> 00:19:03,118
Was it just to buy Bai Yu Tang time?

268
00:19:05,816 --> 00:19:07,039
Or maybe,

269
00:19:07,816 --> 00:19:10,941
he wanted to cover up his real reason for going into the mountains.

270
00:19:46,856 --> 00:19:49,022
Come out, Lord Zhan.

271
00:20:00,495 --> 00:20:02,055
Thank you for leading the way, Lord Hu.

272
00:20:02,536 --> 00:20:04,262
Lord Zhan, you really are clever.

273
00:20:04,438 --> 00:20:06,024
But even if you dig up the Lin residence,

274
00:20:06,048 --> 00:20:07,112
what good will it do?

275
00:20:14,415 --> 00:20:15,776
- Come out. - Come out.

276
00:20:22,816 --> 00:20:26,181
If Lord Zhan insists on entering the Lin residence, go ahead and try.

277
00:20:26,695 --> 00:20:29,861
You'll have to step over me and these people.

278
00:20:47,063 --> 00:20:48,063
Huo Ling Long.

279
00:20:57,255 --> 00:21:01,181
Did you not listen to a word of what Shao Ji Zu said that day?

280
00:21:02,016 --> 00:21:04,181
I suggest you really think about what he said.

281
00:21:04,415 --> 00:21:07,181
Once you figure it out, just go back to the Huo family.

282
00:21:17,136 --> 00:21:18,621
He's just bluffing.

283
00:21:20,563 --> 00:21:21,563
Let's go.

284
00:21:26,552 --> 00:21:28,393
Ma'am, in order to solve the case,

285
00:21:28,474 --> 00:21:31,114
we had no choice but to disturb Shi Lang's peace in the afterlife.

286
00:21:31,215 --> 00:21:32,438
Thank you for understanding.

287
00:21:33,298 --> 00:21:34,983
If the case can be solved,

288
00:21:35,495 --> 00:21:38,815
Shi Lang and his wife can finally rest in peace.

289
00:21:38,895 --> 00:21:40,621
They won't blame you.

290
00:21:41,201 --> 00:21:43,281
I'll go visit my eldest son's house on Front Street.

291
00:21:43,355 --> 00:21:44,875
You can go ahead with the examination.

292
00:21:52,855 --> 00:21:53,855
She said

293
00:21:54,230 --> 00:21:56,410
the young men who worked with Shi Lang back then

294
00:21:56,707 --> 00:21:58,471
had no one to claim their bodies after they died.

295
00:21:58,495 --> 00:22:00,901
So, the authorities buried them all in the mass grave.

296
00:22:01,136 --> 00:22:03,638
So, I went there myself and brought back two bodies.

297
00:22:37,016 --> 00:22:38,136
I noticed something strange.

298
00:22:38,855 --> 00:22:40,122
I examined all the bodies in the mass grave.

299
00:22:40,146 --> 00:22:42,836
All the tooth roots of every single body were blackened.

300
00:22:42,897 --> 00:22:44,039
That can't be a coincidence.

301
00:22:44,423 --> 00:22:46,423
But it doesn't look like they died from poisoning.

302
00:22:46,616 --> 00:22:48,878
The rest of their bodies showed no signs of poisoning.

303
00:22:49,280 --> 00:22:51,816
I've worked cases with the prince and seen coroners examine bodies.

304
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:53,000
People who die from poisoning

305
00:22:53,730 --> 00:22:55,938
always have black marks on their ribs.

306
00:22:56,376 --> 00:22:59,421
Yes. But these people only had a small black spot on their teeth.

307
00:22:59,772 --> 00:23:02,298
Even if it was poison, it wasn't anything deadly.

308
00:23:02,655 --> 00:23:03,878
What else could it be?

309
00:23:04,455 --> 00:23:05,735
Could it be from making elixirs?

310
00:23:06,096 --> 00:23:07,335
I've heard people say

311
00:23:07,415 --> 00:23:08,792
those desperate to become immortals

312
00:23:08,816 --> 00:23:10,941
often burn cinnabar to make elixirs.

313
00:23:11,022 --> 00:23:13,343
Burning cinnabar releases mercury.

314
00:23:13,424 --> 00:23:14,824
Mercury evaporates easily.

315
00:23:14,905 --> 00:23:16,790
These people breathed it in.

316
00:23:17,175 --> 00:23:18,176
Over time,

317
00:23:18,257 --> 00:23:19,616
their teeth would loosen,

318
00:23:19,735 --> 00:23:21,941
and in severe cases, the roots would turn black.

319
00:23:22,662 --> 00:23:23,662
But that can't be right.

320
00:23:23,813 --> 00:23:24,933
If they were making elixirs,

321
00:23:25,188 --> 00:23:27,839
why would they die from being crushed or falling?

322
00:23:29,230 --> 00:23:30,916
Mercury isn't just used for elixirs.

323
00:23:31,147 --> 00:23:32,427
It's also used to refine metals.

324
00:23:33,537 --> 00:23:36,627
The amalgamation process requires a lot of mercury.

325
00:23:36,847 --> 00:23:38,367
Even with safety measures,

326
00:23:38,438 --> 00:23:40,925
miners still show signs of mild mercury poisoning.

327
00:23:41,376 --> 00:23:42,376
Miners?

328
00:23:43,887 --> 00:23:46,327
That's right. All the victims were young and strong.

329
00:23:46,397 --> 00:23:48,661
Mining often leads to landslides and cave-ins.

330
00:23:49,014 --> 00:23:51,206
Every time there's an accident, a bunch of people die at once.

331
00:23:51,230 --> 00:23:52,997
How do we prove our theory?

332
00:23:55,911 --> 00:23:56,911
Test their hair.

333
00:24:05,415 --> 00:24:06,415
It's gold.

334
00:24:14,938 --> 00:24:17,538
There's gold dust on this corpse's hair, too.

335
00:24:18,376 --> 00:24:21,376
No wonder these people are so willing to risk their lives for Hu Xiao Chen.

336
00:24:21,470 --> 00:24:24,150
Turns out the mountain behind Wanshan County is hiding a gold mine.

337
00:24:24,272 --> 00:24:27,073
No wonder in just two years, Wanshan County has changed so much.

338
00:24:27,147 --> 00:24:29,732
These people can easily come up with hundreds of taels of silver

339
00:24:29,813 --> 00:24:31,933
just to arrange a ghost marriage for their relatives.

340
00:24:41,397 --> 00:24:42,397
Ling Long,

341
00:24:42,772 --> 00:24:44,932
you've actually misunderstood something all along.

342
00:24:45,056 --> 00:24:46,945
You thought our families' marriage alliance

343
00:24:47,022 --> 00:24:49,102
was because I wanted the Huo family's Linglong Eye.

344
00:24:49,183 --> 00:24:50,183
But that's not the case.

345
00:24:50,423 --> 00:24:51,869
I'm not the only one with an agenda.

346
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:54,601
I, the prince,

347
00:24:55,336 --> 00:24:56,822
and the Huo family.

348
00:24:57,975 --> 00:25:00,421
All three of us are just getting what we want.

349
00:25:00,935 --> 00:25:02,421
But you're a Huo family member.

350
00:25:02,605 --> 00:25:04,965
So, you and Zhan Zhao are destined to walk different paths.

351
00:25:05,136 --> 00:25:08,897
I've tried to talk you out of investigating with Zhan Zhao so many times,

352
00:25:08,978 --> 00:25:10,036
but you wouldn't listen.

353
00:25:10,117 --> 00:25:12,124
You put yourself in this impossible situation.

354
00:25:13,255 --> 00:25:16,222
You pushed the Huo family to the edge.

355
00:25:20,559 --> 00:25:21,574
Brother.

356
00:25:21,655 --> 00:25:22,655
Ling Long.

357
00:25:22,772 --> 00:25:25,053
The matter of identifying people had already been leaked.

358
00:25:25,495 --> 00:25:27,342
Shao Ji Zu purposely lured me here.

359
00:25:27,559 --> 00:25:28,776
He also misled you with his words

360
00:25:28,800 --> 00:25:30,999
and made you think I was Zhao Yue An.

361
00:25:31,495 --> 00:25:33,239
Don't let what he said get to you.

362
00:25:36,376 --> 00:25:39,255
You don't even trust your brother now?

363
00:25:41,016 --> 00:25:43,461
Of course, I trust that you're not Zhao Yue An.

364
00:25:43,813 --> 00:25:45,173
But what Shao Ji Zu said

365
00:25:45,272 --> 00:25:47,337
wasn't just about proving you're Zhao Yue An.

366
00:25:48,856 --> 00:25:51,072
He said all three sides are just getting what they want from...

367
00:25:51,096 --> 00:25:52,696
If Shao Ji Zu is doing everything he can

368
00:25:52,730 --> 00:25:54,191
to trick you into coming back for the wedding,

369
00:25:54,215 --> 00:25:56,336
he'll use any dirty trick he can think of.

370
00:25:57,022 --> 00:25:58,708
If you keep overthinking his words,

371
00:25:58,938 --> 00:26:00,538
you're just falling right into his trap.

372
00:26:01,438 --> 00:26:03,838
At the banquet earlier, I was worried he'd set up an ambush.

373
00:26:04,016 --> 00:26:05,079
So to keep him calm,

374
00:26:05,175 --> 00:26:07,575
I said the Huo family agreed to the marriage.

375
00:26:07,655 --> 00:26:08,655
Don't take it seriously.

376
00:26:09,512 --> 00:26:11,111
Father asked me to tell you something.

377
00:26:11,188 --> 00:26:12,188
He said,

378
00:26:12,522 --> 00:26:14,082
even if the prince grants the marriage,

379
00:26:14,376 --> 00:26:17,101
a Huo family daughter has the right and confidence to refuse.

380
00:26:17,768 --> 00:26:20,112
If you don't want to get married, don't come back to the Huo family.

381
00:26:20,136 --> 00:26:22,455
As for Shao Ji Zu, Father can explain it to him.

382
00:26:25,856 --> 00:26:27,701
Why did Father suddenly change his mind?

383
00:26:29,895 --> 00:26:30,999
You know how he is.

384
00:26:32,096 --> 00:26:34,135
Every time you throw a tantrum,

385
00:26:34,215 --> 00:26:35,359
he always gives in to you.

386
00:26:36,096 --> 00:26:37,736
He always acts tough but is soft-hearted.

387
00:26:38,188 --> 00:26:39,628
He cares about you more than anyone.

388
00:26:46,695 --> 00:26:47,695
Zhan.

389
00:26:50,772 --> 00:26:53,412
Now that the secret of Wanshan County has finally been revealed,

390
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:54,622
what's the next step?

391
00:26:57,438 --> 00:26:59,005
Bones and gold dust alone

392
00:26:59,272 --> 00:27:02,359
aren't enough to tie Hu Xiao Chen to the gold mine.

393
00:27:03,215 --> 00:27:04,335
We need hard evidence

394
00:27:04,415 --> 00:27:07,342
or a miner willing to testify.

395
00:27:07,735 --> 00:27:09,621
But the miners probably won't come forward.

396
00:27:10,522 --> 00:27:11,624
As for physical evidence,

397
00:27:12,730 --> 00:27:14,216
we have to find the gold mine itself.

398
00:27:16,376 --> 00:27:18,056
Wanshan County is surrounded by mountains.

399
00:27:18,136 --> 00:27:21,336
Trying to find a gold mine in those endless mountains won't be easy.

400
00:27:23,935 --> 00:27:25,822
Those endless mountains...

401
00:27:27,096 --> 00:27:28,118
The Lin estate.

402
00:27:28,449 --> 00:27:32,138
If I'm not mistaken, that's probably where Hu Xiao Chen is hiding the gold.

403
00:27:33,016 --> 00:27:35,181
A secluded mansion hidden in the mountains.

404
00:27:36,296 --> 00:27:38,336
It couldn't be a more perfect spot for hiding gold.

405
00:27:38,605 --> 00:27:39,891
The gold from Wanshan County

406
00:27:40,147 --> 00:27:42,147
keeps flowing straight to the Prince of Xiangyang.

407
00:27:42,438 --> 00:27:44,485
It's funding his rebellion.

408
00:27:44,772 --> 00:27:46,337
There must be a set transport route.

409
00:27:46,695 --> 00:27:47,815
If we follow the Lin estate,

410
00:27:47,935 --> 00:27:50,495
we should be able to find the Prince of Xiangyang's secret base.

411
00:28:29,480 --> 00:28:31,805
I'll personally transport this batch of gold.

412
00:28:33,455 --> 00:28:34,735
You just follow from a distance.

413
00:28:36,032 --> 00:28:37,592
Once you meet up with Feng Shao,

414
00:28:37,689 --> 00:28:38,791
pull back.

415
00:28:40,455 --> 00:28:42,181
Then, go contact Zhou Ji Liang for me.

416
00:29:02,605 --> 00:29:04,291
Dong Jun has failed Your Highness's trust.

417
00:29:04,688 --> 00:29:05,871
I'm here to admit my guilt.

418
00:29:09,695 --> 00:29:13,101
I'm not someone who forgets a loyal person.

419
00:29:14,536 --> 00:29:16,181
Of the four Great Lords,

420
00:29:17,856 --> 00:29:20,782
you and the Mountain Ghost clan have contributed the most.

421
00:29:21,382 --> 00:29:25,090
Why would I erase all your past achievements

422
00:29:25,230 --> 00:29:28,236
over a single mistake?

423
00:29:29,056 --> 00:29:31,655
Come, sit down.

424
00:29:37,527 --> 00:29:39,287
Here's the inventory for this batch of gold.

425
00:29:39,368 --> 00:29:40,728
Please take a look, Your Highness.

426
00:29:50,655 --> 00:29:53,582
You personally escorted this shipment of gold here

427
00:29:54,856 --> 00:29:56,461
to admit your fault

428
00:29:56,735 --> 00:29:59,621
and also to ask for help.

429
00:30:03,313 --> 00:30:05,673
Your Highness, I have a good plan

430
00:30:05,754 --> 00:30:08,217
to get rid of Zhan Zhao for good.

431
00:30:08,495 --> 00:30:09,559
But...

432
00:30:10,296 --> 00:30:12,582
I'll need someone from your manor to help.

433
00:30:13,536 --> 00:30:15,222
The name Zhan Zhao

434
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:20,006
is one I've grown truly sick of hearing.

435
00:30:20,536 --> 00:30:23,861
He Bo and Siming both claimed

436
00:30:24,376 --> 00:30:26,381
they had ways to deal with him.

437
00:30:28,975 --> 00:30:29,999
And what happened?

438
00:30:31,647 --> 00:30:34,934
I created the four Great Lords

439
00:30:35,355 --> 00:30:38,105
to help me achieve greatness,

440
00:30:38,480 --> 00:30:41,284
not to waste time

441
00:30:42,270 --> 00:30:45,063
fighting Zhan Zhao.

442
00:30:46,563 --> 00:30:49,941
I'm working on a foolproof plan

443
00:30:50,520 --> 00:30:51,703
to take a different approach

444
00:30:52,056 --> 00:30:55,461
and get around this obstacle named Zhan Zhao.

445
00:30:57,938 --> 00:30:59,543
May I ask what you mean, Your Highness?

446
00:31:00,576 --> 00:31:02,502
The time isn't right yet.

447
00:31:03,415 --> 00:31:04,559
When the time comes,

448
00:31:04,935 --> 00:31:06,782
I'll let you know for sure.

449
00:31:07,856 --> 00:31:09,901
All the gold in this building,

450
00:31:10,935 --> 00:31:13,135
plus what you've brought this time,

451
00:31:13,215 --> 00:31:16,982
still isn't nearly enough to pave the way for our cause.

452
00:31:18,976 --> 00:31:20,575
Once I return to Wanshan County,

453
00:31:20,647 --> 00:31:22,408
I'll have the miners work through the night.

454
00:31:22,480 --> 00:31:23,726
There's no time.

455
00:31:24,096 --> 00:31:25,381
Within three days,

456
00:31:25,776 --> 00:31:29,036
you need to double the amount.

457
00:31:29,230 --> 00:31:30,230
Three days?

458
00:31:31,022 --> 00:31:32,022
That...

459
00:31:32,605 --> 00:31:33,852
How is that even possible?

460
00:31:34,272 --> 00:31:39,158
Maybe we can use what's already in the county for now.

461
00:31:40,376 --> 00:31:41,376
Your Highness...

462
00:31:41,856 --> 00:31:44,342
All the gold in the county has already been moved here.

463
00:31:46,730 --> 00:31:48,815
Are you talking about...

464
00:31:52,952 --> 00:31:53,975
Your Highness.

465
00:31:54,056 --> 00:31:55,421
Forgive me for being blunt,

466
00:31:55,772 --> 00:31:57,251
the people's share

467
00:31:57,313 --> 00:31:59,576
was earned by every family risking their lives.

468
00:32:00,063 --> 00:32:01,903
Asking them to give up their hard-earned money

469
00:32:02,647 --> 00:32:04,413
isn't something we can do.

470
00:32:05,784 --> 00:32:06,927
Sit down.

471
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:21,463
Don't forget.

472
00:32:22,616 --> 00:32:25,022
Without my gold mine,

473
00:32:26,105 --> 00:32:30,831
Wanshan County would still be full of starving people.

474
00:32:31,536 --> 00:32:34,901
How could they risk their lives otherwise?

475
00:32:47,735 --> 00:32:48,918
Have some tea.

476
00:32:53,008 --> 00:32:56,093
There are some things others can't do,

477
00:32:56,336 --> 00:32:58,456
but you always find a way.

478
00:32:58,559 --> 00:33:04,422
Everyone answers your call in Wanshan County, Lord Hu.

479
00:33:07,784 --> 00:33:08,857
How about this?

480
00:33:08,938 --> 00:33:14,935
Consider this money a loan from your Wanshan County.

481
00:33:16,105 --> 00:33:17,105
What do you think?

482
00:33:17,455 --> 00:33:20,101
I can write up an IOU right now.

483
00:33:22,175 --> 00:33:23,535
You must be joking, Your Highness.

484
00:33:24,096 --> 00:33:25,118
But...

485
00:33:25,415 --> 00:33:28,101
If Wanshan County helps you raise this money,

486
00:33:28,576 --> 00:33:29,678
then Your Highness

487
00:33:30,495 --> 00:33:33,181
needs to solve the county's current troubles first.

488
00:33:34,175 --> 00:33:37,262
I can give you the person you want.

489
00:33:37,536 --> 00:33:41,461
But I don't know what you need this person for.

490
00:33:41,816 --> 00:33:44,470
Is it to negotiate with Zhan Zhao?

491
00:33:45,136 --> 00:33:46,582
I doubt Zhan Zhao

492
00:33:47,376 --> 00:33:50,701
would agree to your terms.

493
00:33:50,897 --> 00:33:51,897
Your Highness...

494
00:33:52,336 --> 00:33:54,976
There's no deal that can't be made in this world.

495
00:33:55,056 --> 00:33:59,022
It all depends on whether we hit Zhan Zhao right where it hurts.

496
00:33:59,655 --> 00:34:00,736
A few days ago,

497
00:34:00,816 --> 00:34:02,901
when I put Zhou Ji Liang to use,

498
00:34:03,296 --> 00:34:06,222
didn't I mention an old story about Zhan Zhao?

499
00:34:07,455 --> 00:34:09,381
Lord Hu really is

500
00:34:09,935 --> 00:34:12,421
Zhan Zhao's old classmate.

501
00:34:13,096 --> 00:34:16,542
You know exactly where to hit his weak spot.

502
00:34:17,776 --> 00:34:21,542
But you should've told me sooner.

503
00:34:22,175 --> 00:34:26,621
That way, I could've saved myself a lot of trouble.

504
00:34:29,415 --> 00:34:33,141
Didn't you also keep Zhao Yue An's fake death from me, Your Highness?

505
00:34:34,016 --> 00:34:35,016
That day,

506
00:34:35,096 --> 00:34:38,101
Zhan Zhao really caught me completely off guard.

507
00:34:49,064 --> 00:34:51,982
Since you already have a plan,

508
00:34:53,975 --> 00:34:57,262
go to my manor and get the person you need.

509
00:35:02,143 --> 00:35:03,287
Thank you, Your Highness.

510
00:35:03,480 --> 00:35:05,525
I'll take my leave now.

511
00:35:07,735 --> 00:35:12,101
What you're holding in your hands is my lifeline.

512
00:35:12,935 --> 00:35:14,502
If you fail again,

513
00:35:15,856 --> 00:35:17,742
I'll truly

514
00:35:19,056 --> 00:35:21,141
have nowhere left to turn.

515
00:35:25,536 --> 00:35:26,782
Rest assured, Your Highness.

516
00:36:00,295 --> 00:36:01,496
Have a seat.

517
00:36:01,576 --> 00:36:03,696
There are no outsiders here. No need to be so formal.

518
00:36:03,815 --> 00:36:04,815
Sit down.

519
00:36:12,936 --> 00:36:13,936
Just now,

520
00:36:14,607 --> 00:36:16,453
you heard everything

521
00:36:17,855 --> 00:36:19,038
I told Lord Dong.

522
00:36:19,936 --> 00:36:20,936
Yes.

523
00:36:21,255 --> 00:36:23,622
Hu Xiao Chen is getting more and more out of line.

524
00:36:24,255 --> 00:36:27,182
He treats Wanshan County like his own little kingdom.

525
00:36:27,456 --> 00:36:29,142
He doesn't respect you at all.

526
00:36:29,522 --> 00:36:31,887
Your Highness, you've been so patient with him

527
00:36:32,536 --> 00:36:35,478
just to buy yourself some extra time, right?

528
00:36:37,605 --> 00:36:40,874
The silver from Wanshan County is just a drop in the bucket.

529
00:36:41,605 --> 00:36:42,926
Your marriage

530
00:36:43,007 --> 00:36:44,533
is the main event.

531
00:36:44,936 --> 00:36:47,102
You need to hurry up.

532
00:36:47,815 --> 00:36:48,815
Yes.

533
00:36:51,496 --> 00:36:52,742
Since Lord Dong

534
00:36:53,313 --> 00:36:54,758
already has a plan,

535
00:36:55,772 --> 00:36:58,799
I'll add something extra to his scheme.

536
00:36:59,896 --> 00:37:01,662
Let him take that person away

537
00:37:02,647 --> 00:37:03,830
and deliver a message for me.

538
00:37:04,355 --> 00:37:05,761
Have you made up your mind

539
00:37:06,655 --> 00:37:08,861
to go all out?

540
00:37:09,096 --> 00:37:11,342
I've already given enough face.

541
00:37:11,735 --> 00:37:12,918
I'm done being generous.

542
00:37:13,605 --> 00:37:15,692
Lord Dong wants to use an old case

543
00:37:16,355 --> 00:37:17,578
against Zhan Zhao.

544
00:37:18,355 --> 00:37:19,835
But if he acts alone,

545
00:37:19,938 --> 00:37:21,983
he won't get very far.

546
00:37:22,272 --> 00:37:23,632
You can help him behind the scenes

547
00:37:23,713 --> 00:37:25,193
to give him a boost.

548
00:37:25,272 --> 00:37:26,375
Let this fire

549
00:37:27,033 --> 00:37:28,639
burn even hotter.

550
00:37:53,528 --> 00:37:55,695
He just tried Blood-Sealing Poison.

551
00:37:57,136 --> 00:37:59,182
Eat it, and you die instantly.

552
00:37:59,576 --> 00:38:00,719
That's boring.

553
00:38:02,272 --> 00:38:03,375
You try this one instead.

554
00:38:04,616 --> 00:38:05,941
Hundred Dragons Entwined.

555
00:38:21,175 --> 00:38:22,861
I heard Lord Hu was looking for me.

556
00:38:23,056 --> 00:38:24,136
So, I came to wait for you.

557
00:38:25,335 --> 00:38:27,342
Too bad you showed up a bit late, Lord Hu.

558
00:38:27,576 --> 00:38:31,182
You missed seeing your men begging me for mercy.

559
00:38:31,496 --> 00:38:32,496
What a shame.

560
00:38:33,016 --> 00:38:36,622
Who gave you the guts to cause trouble in my county office?

561
00:38:43,272 --> 00:38:44,272
Hu Xiao Chen.

562
00:38:44,576 --> 00:38:46,742
I'm not Mo Dao from before.

563
00:38:47,255 --> 00:38:49,775
I won't come running just because you call.

564
00:38:49,855 --> 00:38:52,142
I won't play along with you unconditionally.

565
00:38:52,976 --> 00:38:55,061
About you killing my men earlier,

566
00:38:55,335 --> 00:38:57,102
if you don't give me an explanation today,

567
00:38:57,416 --> 00:38:59,936
I'll wipe out everyone in your office.

568
00:39:00,255 --> 00:39:01,438
They'll die with my men.

569
00:39:06,695 --> 00:39:09,159
You think you're smarter than Mo Dao?

570
00:39:09,536 --> 00:39:11,248
Just grabbing a few people to test the poison

571
00:39:11,272 --> 00:39:13,513
and killing a few of my men is enough for you?

572
00:39:14,335 --> 00:39:16,255
I've got something important for you to handle.

573
00:39:18,605 --> 00:39:20,252
Don't you love killing people?

574
00:39:20,791 --> 00:39:22,198
I'll give you a chance.

575
00:39:22,813 --> 00:39:23,955
How many you kill

576
00:39:24,772 --> 00:39:26,378
depends on your skills.

577
00:39:28,536 --> 00:39:29,536
Fine.

578
00:39:29,976 --> 00:39:30,976
Let's hear it.

579
00:39:45,192 --> 00:39:47,355
Stop. Who goes there?

580
00:40:25,456 --> 00:40:26,822
Why are you up so early?

581
00:40:29,295 --> 00:40:30,622
I couldn't sleep anyway.

582
00:40:31,183 --> 00:40:33,223
So, I got up to make medicine for the young master.

583
00:40:33,896 --> 00:40:36,112
You've seemed really out of it these past couple of days.

584
00:40:36,136 --> 00:40:37,199
Are you just tired?

585
00:40:41,255 --> 00:40:43,375
Don't tell me you're still thinking about that night.

586
00:40:48,605 --> 00:40:49,683
Honestly,

587
00:40:50,103 --> 00:40:52,223
I don't think the young master has told me the truth.

588
00:40:53,230 --> 00:40:54,717
When he saw Zhou Ji Liang was alive,

589
00:40:54,855 --> 00:40:55,998
he wasn't surprised at all.

590
00:40:56,272 --> 00:40:57,914
He even stayed at the yamen the whole time.

591
00:40:57,938 --> 00:41:00,618
He clearly knew ahead of time that Zhou Ji Liang would look for me.

592
00:41:04,980 --> 00:41:07,066
He doesn't want me to bring up the past anymore.

593
00:41:08,464 --> 00:41:10,230
With his health like this,

594
00:41:11,522 --> 00:41:13,042
I really can't ask him about it again.

595
00:41:14,119 --> 00:41:15,119
If you say that,

596
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:17,331
aren't you basically believing everything Zhou Ji Liang said?

597
00:41:17,355 --> 00:41:18,835
How could you trust anything he says?

598
00:41:25,332 --> 00:41:26,691
Didn't you see the case file?

599
00:41:26,772 --> 00:41:28,937
In the file, how was my family's case recorded?

600
00:41:29,433 --> 00:41:30,633
Was there anything suspicious?

601
00:41:30,921 --> 00:41:32,983
Nothing suspicious. Don't overthink it.

602
00:41:33,335 --> 00:41:34,695
Yaksha is back!

603
00:41:34,775 --> 00:41:36,981
Yaksha's back to punish the wicked!

604
00:41:37,775 --> 00:41:39,061
Yaksha is back!

605
00:41:39,813 --> 00:41:40,996
Ming Zhu Er!

606
00:41:41,272 --> 00:41:42,335
Ming Zhu Er!

607
00:41:44,397 --> 00:41:45,397
Lord Zhan!

608
00:41:45,687 --> 00:41:46,687
Something's happened!

609
00:41:49,272 --> 00:41:51,558
Was he really hanged by Lord Yaksha?

610
00:41:52,215 --> 00:41:53,512
Someone saw it happen last night.

611
00:41:53,536 --> 00:41:54,716
There's no doubt about it.

612
00:41:55,016 --> 00:41:56,038
Who is this guy?

613
00:41:56,456 --> 00:41:58,456
Who? Corrupt officials.

614
00:41:59,056 --> 00:42:00,776
None of the people Yaksha punished is good.

615
00:42:00,815 --> 00:42:03,248
He is wanted for a major crime but they never managed to catch him.

616
00:42:03,272 --> 00:42:04,592
A clerk from Xiangzhou Prefecture.

617
00:42:04,616 --> 00:42:06,518
Look, it's written clearly up there.

618
00:42:07,175 --> 00:42:08,822
This guy really is rotten to the core.

619
00:42:09,263 --> 00:42:10,509
The authorities are useless.

620
00:42:10,605 --> 00:42:12,193
They've been after him forever and still can't catch him.

621
00:42:12,217 --> 00:42:13,657
Only Lord Yaksha could handle it.

622
00:42:13,775 --> 00:42:15,112
Now things are finally looking up.

623
00:42:15,136 --> 00:42:17,695
After ten years, Lord Yaksha finally took action again.

624
00:42:17,775 --> 00:42:19,775
He came to our county to uphold justice,

625
00:42:19,855 --> 00:42:21,032
get rid of evil, and protect the innocent.

626
00:42:21,056 --> 00:42:22,816
Only when Siming has been brought to justice

627
00:42:22,976 --> 00:42:24,581
will your aunt and my brother's case

628
00:42:25,016 --> 00:42:26,541
be put to rest.

629
00:42:31,775 --> 00:42:32,936
Move aside!

630
00:42:33,016 --> 00:42:34,336
Official business, clear the way.

631
00:42:34,496 --> 00:42:35,496
Move aside!

632
00:42:37,022 --> 00:42:38,661
Hurry up and go!

633
00:42:39,096 --> 00:42:40,096
Move faster!

634
00:42:47,272 --> 00:42:48,873
I am Zhan Zhao from the Kaifeng Tribunal.

635
00:42:48,897 --> 00:42:51,097
I'm here in Xiangzhou by imperial order to investigate.

636
00:42:51,272 --> 00:42:53,688
This person is closely tied to my case.

637
00:42:54,071 --> 00:42:55,311
Let me ask him a few questions.
